                        "text": "<h3><strong>UK Shipping</strong></h3><p><a href=\"https://www.urbanindustry.co.uk/pages/uk-shipping\">Click here</a> for our UK shipping rates - Standard, Free and Next Day Options. All orders placed Monday - Friday before 15:00pm GMT will be dispatched same day.</p><h3><strong>EU Shipping</strong></h3><p>We sell to EU Countries with ALL DUTIES PAID. (DDP) Urban Industry now take care of all of your own countries TAX, Duties and Admin Fees so you can just order and take delivery! There are NO EXTRA FEES to pay other than the price you see and the shipping.</p><p>We ship to almost all of Europe using DHL. All Euro prices are now FREE of UK VAT.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.urbanindustry.co.uk/pages/european-shipping\">European Shipping rates - Click here</a></p><h3><strong>Worldwide Shipping</strong></h3><p>We ship around the world FAST using DHL.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.urbanindustry.co.uk/pages/worldwide_shipping_1\">World Wide Shipping rates - Click here</a></p>",
