                    "text_JEb7iz": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<h3>UK Returns</h3><h3>Returns Period</h3><p>We allow 18 days from point of arrival with you to return your order to us. For hygiene reasons we cannot accept returns for underwear, cosmetics or socks unless faulty. For our full <a href=\"https://www.urbanindustry.co.uk/pages/uk_returns\">UK returns policy click here</a></p><p>If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase or need to return an item for any reason, simply return the items to us in their original condition and packaging within 18 days of receipt and we will issue you with a refund/exchange or store credit</p><p><a href=\"https://www.urbanindustry.co.uk/a/returns\">Click here</a> to use our returns portal to track the items back to us</p><h3>International Returns</h3><p>If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase or need to return an item for any reason, simply return the items to us in their original condition and packaging within 18 days of delivery to you and we will issue you with a refund</p><p><a href=\"https://www.urbanindustry.co.uk/pages/international-returns\">Click here</a> for more information on returns</p>",
